libg15
------------------------------------------
Library to handle the LCD and extra keys on the Logitech G15 Gaming Keyboard
and similar devices

Runtime requirements:
  cygwin-2.9.0-2
  libg15-devel-1.2.7-1bl3
  libg15_1-1.2.7-1bl3
  libusb0-1.2.6.0-2
  pkg-config-0.29.1-1

Build requirements:
(besides corresponding -devel packages)
  autoconf-13-1
  automake-9-1
  binutils-2.28-3
  cygport-0.24.1-1
  gcc-core-6.4.0-1
  libtool-2.4.6-4
  make-4.2.1-2

Canonical website:
  https://sf.net/projects/g15tools/

Canonical download:
  mirror://sourceforge/g15tools/libg15-1.2.7.tar.bz2

-------------------------------------------

Build instructions:
  1. unpack libg15-1.2.7-X-src.tar.xz
  2. if you use setup to install this src package,
     it will be unpacked under /usr/src automatically
        % cd /usr/src
        % cygport ./libg15-1.2.7-X.cygport all

This will create:
  /usr/src/libg15-1.2.7-X-src.tar.xz
  /usr/src/libg15-1.2.7-X.tar.xz
  /usr/src/libg15_1-1.2.7-X.tar.xz
  /usr/src/libg15-devel-1.2.7-X.tar.xz

-------------------------------------------

Files included in the binary package:

(libg15)
  /usr/share/doc/Cygwin/libg15.README
  /usr/share/doc/libg15/AUTHORS
  /usr/share/doc/libg15/COPYING
  /usr/share/doc/libg15/ChangeLog
  /usr/share/doc/libg15/NEWS
  /usr/share/doc/libg15/README

(libg15_1)
  /usr/bin/cygg15-1.dll

(libg15-devel)
  /usr/include/libg15.h
  /usr/lib/libg15.dll.a
  /usr/lib/pkgconfig/libg15.pc

------------------

Port Notes:

----- version 1.2.7-1bl3 -----
Rebuild with gcc-6.4.0

----- version 1.2.7-1bl2 -----
Rebuild on x86_64

----- version 1.2.7-1bl1 -----
